Data Collection Method: NCDOT Count Assignments 12-07125 thru 12-07138 were counted over a two day
period, with one counter assigned to each zone (aka count assignment) of the SR 1340 (Prospect Road)/North
Odum Street corridor. Counters used Jamar count boards to count pedestrians crossing east to west and west
to east across Prospect Road/North Odum Street within their zone. Each zone was marked in the field with a
traffic cone. See page 3 for a map of the complete study area & a summary of the 14 zones counted.
